    <h3>AI Credit System</h3>
    <p>All premium AI features on Canva share a single monthly credit pool. On Pro (approximately 500 credits per month), each AI operation — a Dream Lab generation, a Magic Write session, an AI video creation — consumes from this pool. Heavy users may hit the ceiling. An "AI Pass" paid add-on is available for 40x more AI usage on Pro and Business plans for users who need more. The Free plan provides roughly 200 Standard AI uses or 20 Premium AI uses per month, sufficient for occasional testing but not regular content production.</p>

    <h3>Pricing Analysis</h3>
    <p>At $15/month for Pro (or ~$12/month billed annually), Canva AI offers exceptional bundled value: design editor + AI tools + 141M+ premium stock assets + 3.6M+ templates + the free Affinity professional suite. Compare this to piecing together separate tools: Midjourney ($10-60/mo) for images + ChatGPT ($20/mo) for copy + Photoshop ($23/mo) for editing = $53-103/mo for comparable capability. Canva's weakness is that no single AI feature matches the dedicated tools — but if convenience and cost matter more than peak quality, the value proposition is hard to beat.</p>

