    <h3>Core Workflow: How Magic Studio Works</h3>
    <p>Magic Studio is embedded in the existing Canva editor — there is no separate app or mode. Users design normally and invoke AI tools as needed: click "Magic" to generate, edit, or transform content. The AI reads the active design's brand kit and context, generates results in-place, and allows immediate refinement.</p>

