    <p>Sign-up happens directly through the Canva website at <a href="https://www.canva.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer sponsored">canva.com</a>. The Free plan is a permanent tier — not a trial — and includes 1.6M+ free templates, 4.7M+ free stock assets, 5 GB storage, and approximately 200 AI uses per month. No credit card is required.</p>
