  <section id="verdict">
    <h2>Final Assessment</h2>

    <p>Canva AI (Magic Studio) is the most practical AI design suite for non-designers — not because any single feature is remarkable, but because everything works in one place with your brand applied automatically. For our audience of affiliate marketers, content creators, and small business owners, the question is not "is Canva AI better than Midjourney?" — it is "does Canva AI save me enough time to justify the Pro upgrade?" For most people producing 5+ branded graphics per week, the answer is yes.</p>

    <p>The limitations matter: AI features are gated behind Pro, the credit pool caps heavy usage, and template homogeneity is a real concern for brand differentiation. But the bundled value — design editor + 25+ AI tools + 141M+ premium assets + free Affinity suite — at ~$12/month with annual billing is unmatched in the design software market.</p>

